Introduction to Computer System

Computer is a binary digital system.

What does binary mean? What does digital mean?

What is a bit? It is a basic unit of info in a computer.

BIt is a contraction of two words.
BIT = Binary Digit


n bit to represent 2^n possible things.

Why use a binary system?

Either on or off. or voltage present or voltage absent.

